{"article_id":"bg0ITncIngSkAL53","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Mueller Report Does n't Find Russian Collusion ,","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"But Ca n't 'Exonerate ' On Obstruction","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"Special counsel Robert Mueller did not find evidence","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"that President Trump 's campaign conspired with Russia","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"to influence the 2016 election ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"according to a summary of findings","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"submitted to Congress by Attorney General William Barr .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"`` The Special Counsel 's investigation did not find","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"that the Trump campaign or anyone","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"associated with it","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"conspired or coordinated with Russia in its efforts","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"to influence the 2016 U.S. presidential election , ''","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Barr wrote in a letter to leaders of the House and Senate judiciary committees on Sunday afternoon .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"That was despite `` multiple offers from Russian-affiliated individuals","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"to assist the Trump campaign , ''","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"he wrote .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"However , Mueller 's investigation did not take a position","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"on whether Trump obstructed justice","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"by trying to frustrate the ongoing investigation .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"`` [ W ] hile this report does not conclude","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"that the President committed a crime ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"it also does not exonerate him , ''","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Barr quotes from Mueller 's report .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"The attorney general wrote","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"that he and Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein had concluded","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"that the findings of the special counsel were `` not sufficient","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"to establish","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"that the president committed an obstruction-of-justice offense . ''","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"The Justice Department leaders reached that conclusion ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Barr wrote ,","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"without regard to the `` constitutional considerations ''","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"that surround","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"whether the department can seek an indictment of a sitting president .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Trump talked with reporters","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"as he prepared to return from Florida to the White House ,","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"calling the investigation `` an illegal take-down","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"that failed . ''","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"`` It was just announced there was no collusion with Russia , the most ridiculous thing","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"I 've ever heard .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"There was no obstruction ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"and it was a complete and total exoneration , ''","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"Trump said","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"before boarding Air Force One .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"`` It 's a shame","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"our country had to go through this ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"and to be honest ,","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"it 's a shame your president had to go through this . ''","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"Trump also said :","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"`` Hopefully someone 's going to look at the other side , ''","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"seeming to revive suggestions","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"that he wanted an investigation into his 2016 Democratic opponent Hillary Clinton ,","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"which he has called for several times .","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"At Trump 's rallies , there are frequent chants of `` Lock her up ! ''","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"FBI Director James Comey announced in 2016","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"that Clinton would not be charged .","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"Trump 's outside attorneys ,","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"including Rudy Giuliani and Jay Sekulow ,","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"released a statement on Sunday","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"hailing what they said","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"was `` a complete and total vindication of the president . ''","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"Top Republicans also seized on the news ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"arguing","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"that Trump has now been absolved .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Senate Judiciary Committee Chairman Lindsey Graham , R-S.C. ,","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"who played golf on Sunday afternoon in Florida with the president ,","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"said in a statement :","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"`` Good day for the rule of law .","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"Great day for President Trump and his team . ''","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"`` The cloud","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"hanging over President Trump","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"has been removed by this report , ''","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"Graham added .","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"`` Bad day for those","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"hoping","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"the Mueller investigation would take President Trump down . ''","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"House Minority Leader Kevin McCarthy , R-Calif. said :","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"`` It is abundantly clear ,","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"without a shadow of a doubt ,","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"there was no collusion ...","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"This case is closed . ''","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Georgia Rep. Doug Collins , the top Republican on the House Judiciary Committee , said","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"Barr 's letter should `` assure every American","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"there was no collusion between Russia and Donald Trump or his campaign . ''","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"`` The special counsel 's investigation was long , thorough and conclusive :","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"There was no collusion .","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"There is no constitutional crisis , ''","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"Collins added .","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"`` As the report states ,","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"'the evidence does not establish","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"that the president was involved in an underlying crime","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"related to Russian election interference . ' ``","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"Collins also urged House Judiciary Committee Chairman Jerry Nadler , D-N.Y. , to `` rethink '' the committee 's ongoing investigations and shift to focus on issues such as immigration and criminal justice reform .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"Nadler , however , was more cautious and seized on the language by Barr","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"that suggests","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"Mueller 's report left in limbo the question","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"of whether Trump obstructed justice .","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"`` Mueller clearly and explicitly is not exonerating the President ,","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"and we must hear from AG Barr about his decision making","depth":15},{"id":98,"text":"and see all the underlying evidence","depth":15},{"id":99,"text":"for the American people to know all the facts , ''","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"Nadler tweeted .","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"He continued :","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"`` There must be full transparency in what Special Counsel Mueller uncovered","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"to not exonerate the President from wrongdoing .","depth":14},{"id":104,"text":"DOJ owes the public more than just a brief synopsis and decision","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"not to go any further in their work . ''","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"Nadler also argued","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"given the 22 months","depth":15},{"id":109,"text":"Mueller spent investigating Trump ,","depth":15},{"id":110,"text":"the two days","depth":16},{"id":111,"text":"that Barr spent","depth":17},{"id":112,"text":"boiling down his work","depth":17},{"id":113,"text":"is not sufficient .","depth":15},{"id":114,"text":"The House Judiciary Committee chairman said","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"he intends to call Barr to testify soon before a hearing .","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi and Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer waited more than two hours after the letter 's release","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"to issue a statement ,","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"writing","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"that it `` raises as many questions","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"as it answers ''","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"and continuing to call for the report 's full release .","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"The Democratic leaders echoed Nadler","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"in pointing out","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"that Barr 's letter notes","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"that Mueller did not exonerate Trump on the question of obstruction .","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"They wrote","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"it `` demonstrates how urgent it is that the full report and underlying documentation be made public","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"without any further delay .","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"Given Mr. Barr 's public record of bias against the Special Counsel 's inquiry ,","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"he is not a neutral observer","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"and is not in a position","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"to make objective determinations about the report . ''","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"Barr wrote","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"that Mueller interviewed about 500 witnesses ,","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"made requests to 13 foreign governments for evidence","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"and obtained more than 230 orders for communications records .","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"He also said","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"that Mueller has n't recommended indictments against anyone else","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"and that there are no sealed indictments","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"that have yet to be made public .","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"The news about no more charges was part of the announcement on Friday","depth":7},{"id":142,"text":"when Mueller notified the leaders of the Justice Department","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"that he had completed his work ,","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"which began in May 2017 .","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"For much of the weekend , Washington has been anticipating the conclusions from Barr ,","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"who spent Saturday and Sunday in his office , along with Rosenstein .","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"According to a senior Justice Department official ,","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"Barr 's chief of staff called White House lawyer Emmet Flood at 3 p.m.","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"to give him a `` readout '' of the letter .","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"Mueller has not been at the Justice Department this weekend ,","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"and he `` was not consulted on this letter , ''","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"according to the department .","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"The Justice Department is not giving a timeline","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"as to when it may release additional material from the Mueller investigation ,","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"and it will review the report and materials for grand jury information and for information","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"that could implicate ongoing investigations .","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"Calls have been nearly universal and bipartisan for Mueller 's original report to be released","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"and for the public or Congress to access its findings and its underlying source material .","depth":8},{"id":159,"text":"Many Republicans and Democrats agree","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"that they will not be content only with a Barr-drafted synopsis of the report .","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"`` It needs to be released to the Congress ,","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"and it needs to be released to the American people , ''","depth":12},{"id":163,"text":"Sen. Ted Cruz , R-Texas , told CNN on Sunday morning .","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"`` This has consumed two years of the American people 's time ,","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"and we need full transparency . ''","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"Congressional Democrats appeared nearly unanimous about the need for wide release ,","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"and individual Democratic leaders also tried to pre-empt what","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"they feared","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"might be attempts by the White House","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"to conceal Mueller 's findings .","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"Specifically , one long-standing question has been whether Trump might seek to invoke executive privilege , the doctrine","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"that allows an administration to keep secret some of its internal workings .","depth":8},{"id":173,"text":"Nadler , the House Judiciary Committee chairman , told NBC on Sunday morning","depth":10},{"id":174,"text":"that he thinks","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"the president should n't attempt it .","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"`` I do not believe","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"it exists here at all","depth":12},{"id":178,"text":"because ,","depth":13},{"id":179,"text":"as we learned from the [ Richard ] Nixon tapes case ,","depth":14},{"id":180,"text":"executive privilege can not be used","depth":15},{"id":181,"text":"to hide wrongdoing , ''","depth":15},{"id":182,"text":"Nadler said .","depth":12},{"id":183,"text":"Continued Nadler :","depth":12},{"id":184,"text":"`` In that case , the Supreme Court , nine to nothing , ordered","depth":13},{"id":185,"text":"that all the claims of executive privilege be overridden","depth":14},{"id":186,"text":"and the tapes be public .","depth":14},{"id":187,"text":"... The president may try to assert it ,","depth":13},{"id":188,"text":"may try to hide things behind it .","depth":13},{"id":189,"text":"But I do n't think","depth":13},{"id":190,"text":"that 's right","depth":14},{"id":191,"text":"or [ will ] be successful . ''","depth":14},{"id":192,"text":"Trump , for his part , has said in the past","depth":10},{"id":193,"text":"both","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"that he does n't mind","depth":14},{"id":195,"text":"if Mueller 's report becomes public","depth":14},{"id":196,"text":"- because","depth":14},{"id":197,"text":"he says","depth":15},{"id":198,"text":"he has done nothing wrong -","depth":15},{"id":199,"text":"and that there should n't have been a Mueller report in the first place .","depth":11},{"id":200,"text":"Trump has gone back and forth about what he accepts about Russian interference in 2016 ,","depth":11},{"id":201,"text":"but he has been consistent","depth":12},{"id":202,"text":"that neither he nor anyone in his campaign had any connection to it .","depth":12},{"id":203,"text":"That idea is a `` hoax ''","depth":11},{"id":204,"text":"perpetuated by conspirators and Democrats","depth":12},{"id":205,"text":"who are sore","depth":15},{"id":206,"text":"that Clinton lost to him ,","depth":15},{"id":207,"text":"Trump says ,","depth":14},{"id":208,"text":"and who have been consequently running a `` witch hunt '' against him .","depth":13}],"relations":[{"parent":417,"left":210,"right":416,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":210,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":416,"left":240,"right":415,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":240,"left":223,"right":239,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":223,"left":214,"right":222,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":212,"right":213,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":2,"right":211,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity"